title: Dad Jokes
description:
* Check out a special filmed version of this sketch here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D9KnN86vc00 *

Written by Jon Bershad
Starring Jonathan Marballi, Lisa Kleinman, Kelly Hudson, Dan Hodapp

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, March 3, 2014.

Filmed by Ryan Hunter and Curtis Raye.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
